::KitKat::



She decided that if a fight was about to happen, she would not interefer.  
She walked quietly along the hillside without making a sound.  She followed 
her nose along a path.
"Hmm, I smell a male wolf.  I hope he won't mind me hunting in his 
terratory."

She kept going untill she found a hole in the ground.  It was a rabbit 
mound.  She waited until it came out.  The rabbit saw her and went back in 
the hole before she could strike.

"Well," she said with a sigh, "looks like that lunch opertunity went out the 
window."
She loped along looking for something else to munch on.
